&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Secondment post as a Clinical Nurse Manager on Fletcher ward – Care of the Elderly ward&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced nurse with substantial experience at a senior level. You must be able to provide visible leadership, role modelling and expert clinical skills in this area and must also be an excellent communicator with the ability to interface with a variety of different groups within the multi-disciplinary team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be a registered nurse and educated to degree or master’s level. Teaching and Assessing qualification is required. He/she will need to have commitment to professional development of nurses and possess the necessary skills: initiative, motivation, supervisory and problem solving. This role is essential in leading and managing a team of nursing who can deliver exceptional patient focused care in the ever changing and challenging clinical environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key responsibilities include managing the nursing workforce, supporting the development of nurses, overseas and new starters in collaboration with the practice development nurse in providing clinical supervision, teaching, identifying and sourcing required training needs for all junior nursing groups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJincy Mary JoseJob titleElderly Care Nurse PractitionerEmail addressjincyjose@nhs.netTelephone number02088695070Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Junierose Gazzingan /Jincy Mary Jose on 07384900672/02088695070 for further details.&lt;/p&gt;
